            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tlamantli tlen tzilini tlen motectoc, motlatihtoc zomotehtequereztihtoc iixco tlen ce achi huapalli ihticacahuatic, motequihuia para ica tlatzotzonazceh zo tlen ica quipehualtia ce tlamantli.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Eastern Huasteca Nahuatl</Note_Language>
